<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cryptohopper is a popular automated crypto trading platform for users who want AI tools, copy trading, DCA features, trailing tools, and support for major exchanges. Its official site describes a platform that combines trading bots, AI, copy trading, and automation for different skill levels.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">One reason Cryptohopper continues to be used by traders in 2026 is that it gives users multiple paths. Beginners can explore templates or copy trading, while experienced traders can build more customized automated strategies. This makes it more flexible than platforms that only focus on one bot type.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cryptohopper is best for users who want a mix of automation, AI-assisted strategy selection, copy trading, and deeper customization over time.</span></p>
